headline: Does Phillips 66 Still Offer Value After Its Multi Year Surge And Recent Pullback In 2025
summary: Wondering if Phillips 66 is still worth buying after its big multi year run, or if the easy money has already been made? This breakdown will help you decide whether the current price makes sense. Despite a strong long term record, with the stock up 128.0% over five years and 21.2% over the last year, recent momentum has cooled. It is down 8.9% in the last week and 3.6% over the past month, even though it remains up 12.7% year to date. Part of the recent share price hesitation reflects...
